          <h3 style={{ margin: '0 0 12px' }}>‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠</h3>
          <div style={{ display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: '1fr auto', gap: 8, fontSize: 14 }}>
