          {/* üè¶ ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ä‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÇ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô */}
          <div style={{
            marginTop: 16,
            padding: '12px 14px',
            border: '1px solid #d1d5db',
            borderRadius: 10,
            background: '#f9fafb',
            fontSize: 14,
            lineHeight: 1.6
          }}>
            <strong style={{ display: 'block', fontSize: 15, marginBottom: 6 }}>üè¶ ‡πÇ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ä‡∏µ</strong>
            <div><strong>‡∏ò‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏≤‡∏£:</strong> ‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏£‡πÑ‡∏ó‡∏¢ (KBank)</div>
            <div><strong>‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ä‡∏µ:</strong> ‡∏®‡∏∏‡∏†‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏¢ ‡∏û‡∏£‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≠‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏£‡πå</div>
            <div><strong>‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏Ç‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ä‡∏µ:</strong> 123-4-56789-0</div>
            <div style={{ color: '#6b7280', marginTop: 4 }}>
              ‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏≤‡πÇ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏¢‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏° ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏õ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏∑‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style={{ marginTop: 16 }}>
            <div style={{ fontSize: 14, marginBottom: 6 }}>‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏õ (‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ)</div>
            <input type="file" accept="image/*" onChange={e=>setSlip(e.target.files?.[0] || null)} />
